translation.Name: France Note - Lost Cargo
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_3: German aircraft has been spotted on our radar 5 km north-east of us. We are taking evasive maneuvers and radio'ing the English for air support.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_5: We have just been torpedoe'd and are sinking! I fear this is the end.. so much for those tanks.
